{NORTH has 17 points and might open 1NT. But with the 5-card Major suit she prefers 
to open 1\S.

SOUTH has good \S support and 10 points, counting 1 for the doubleton \C. 
It is easily worth a raise to 2\S

NORTH cannot bid game yet, after all, SOUTH could have as few as 6 points. But she can 
continue with a 3\S bid in hopes that SOUTH actually has 9 or 10 points.

SOUTH comes through with 4\S.}

